DHACA membership is individual, not corporate, so privacy legislation prevents us from disclosing individual details.&#xd;
&#xd;
As mentioned earlier, our members come from across health &amp; social care: commissioners, providers, sector bodies, regulators and patient groups, together with tech firms ranging from micro SMEs and start-ups to major global brands.&#xd;
&#xd;
Although we are primarily UK-based we have noticed a growing number of members joining from other EU countries.
